---
import MainGridLayout from "@layouts/MainGridLayout.astro";  
---

<MainGridLayout title="来源">
    <div class="card-base p-6 md:p-8">
    <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-black dark:text-white mb-6">来源</h1>

    <p class="text-sm text-black/60 dark:text-white/60 mb-4">
        当前博客的模板与部分功能代码来自以下开源仓库。感谢原作者们的无私奉献与开源贡献。
    </p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
    <a href="https://github.com/saicaca/fuwari" target="_blank" class="repo-card group">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <div class="relative w-5 h-5 rounded overflow-hidden">
                <img src="https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/25200299?v=4" loading="lazy" class="w-full h-full object-cover" alt="saicaca" />
            </div>
            <div class="font-bold text-black dark:text-white group-hover:text-[var(--primary)] transition-colors">saicaca</div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-sm text-black/50 dark:text-white/50 mt-1">✨ 一个用 Astro 构建的静态博客模板。</div>
    </a>

    <a href="https://github.com/afoim/fuwari" target="_blank" class="repo-card group">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <div class="relative w-5 h-5 rounded overflow-hidden">
                <img src="https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/180811437?v=4" loading="lazy" class="w-full h-full object-cover" alt="afoim" />
            </div>
            <div class="font-bold text-black dark:text-white group-hover:text-[var(--primary)] transition-colors">afoim</div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-sm text-black/50 dark:text-white/50 mt-1">魔改版 Fuwari，自用博客。</div>
    </a>

    <a href="https://github.com/Besty0728/fuwari" target="_blank" class="repo-card group">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <div class="relative w-5 h-5 rounded overflow-hidden">
                <img src="https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/199687402?v=4" loading="lazy" class="w-full h-full object-cover" alt="Besty" />
            </div>
            <div class="font-bold text-black dark:text-white group-hover:text-[var(--primary)] transition-colors">Besty</div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-sm text-black/50 dark:text-white/50 mt-1">本仓库来自对fuwari的二次魔改版本的三次魔改</div>
    </a>
</div>